-{"id":"jeffreysprompts.com-2hhc","title":"Implement PWA support with offline viewing","description":"## Origin
Mirror from jeffreysprompts_premium jeffreysprompts_premium-hgv5. Keep both repos in sync.

## Task
Add Progressive Web App support for mobile users with offline capability.

## Why This Matters
- Mobile users expect app-like experience
- Offline access to saved prompts
- Faster repeat visits
- Install to home screen

## Features

### 1. Web App Manifest
```json
{
  "name": "JeffreysPrompts Premium",
  "short_name": "JeffreysPrompts",
  "description": "Your premium prompt library",
  "start_url": "/dashboard",
  "display": "standalone",
  "background_color": "#1a1a2e",
  "theme_color": "#6366f1",
  "icons": [
    { "src": "/icons/192.png", "sizes": "192x192", "type": "image/png" },
    { "src": "/icons/512.png", "sizes": "512x512", "type": "image/png" }
  ]
}
```

### 2. Service Worker
- Cache app shell (HTML, CSS, JS)
- Cache API responses (prompts, collections)
- Network-first for fresh data
- Cache-first for static assets
- Background sync for offline actions

### 3. Offline Capabilities
- View cached prompts offline
- View cached collections
- Queue actions when offline (save, edit)
- Sync when back online
- Clear indicator of offline status

### 4. Install Prompt
- Custom install banner
- Instructions for iOS (Add to Home Screen)
- Track install events

## Implementation

### Service Worker Strategy
```typescript
// sw.ts using Workbox
import { precacheAndRoute } from 'workbox-precaching';
import { registerRoute } from 'workbox-routing';
import { NetworkFirst, CacheFirst, StaleWhileRevalidate } from 'workbox-strategies';

// Precache app shell
precacheAndRoute(self.__WB_MANIFEST);

// API calls - network first with cache fallback
registerRoute(
  ({ url }) => url.pathname.startsWith('/api/prompts'),
  new NetworkFirst({
    cacheName: 'api-prompts',
    plugins: [
      new ExpirationPlugin({ maxEntries: 100, maxAgeSeconds: 86400 })
    ]
  })
);

// Static assets - cache first
registerRoute(
  ({ request }) => request.destination === 'image',
  new CacheFirst({
    cacheName: 'images',
    plugins: [
      new ExpirationPlugin({ maxEntries: 50, maxAgeSeconds: 604800 })
    ]
  })
);
```

### Offline Detection
```typescript
function useOnlineStatus() {
  const [isOnline, setIsOnline] = useState(navigator.onLine);

  useEffect(() => {
    const handleOnline = () => setIsOnline(true);
    const handleOffline = () => setIsOnline(false);

    window.addEventListener('online', handleOnline);
    window.addEventListener('offline', handleOffline);

    return () => {
      window.removeEventListener('online', handleOnline);
      window.removeEventListener('offline', handleOffline);
    };
  }, []);

  return isOnline;
}
```

## Files to Create
- public/manifest.json
- src/lib/pwa/service-worker.ts
- src/lib/pwa/offline-storage.ts
- src/hooks/use-online-status.ts
- src/components/pwa/install-prompt.tsx
- src/components/pwa/offline-indicator.tsx

## Success Criteria
- App installable on mobile
- Prompts viewable offline
- Actions sync when back online
- Lighthouse PWA score > 90
